## Architecture Decisions

| Decision | Choice | Rationale |
|---|---|---|
| **Layout** | `src/` layout | Prevents import contamination; tests run against installed package |
| **Build backend** | Hatchling + hatch-vcs | Fast, standards-compliant (PEP 517/621); version from Git tags |
| **Package manager** | uv | 10-100x faster than pip; deterministic lockfile |
| **Linter + Formatter** | Ruff | Replaces Flake8 + Black + isort + Bandit in one Rust binary |
| **Type checker** | Pyright (strict) | Faster than mypy; better inference; strict mode = no implicit `Any` |
{% if include_ci and include_github -%}
| **CI** | GitHub Actions DAG | Fail-fast: Lint → Format → Types → Tests |
{%- endif %}
{% if include_pypi_publish and include_github -%}
| **Publishing** | OIDC Trusted Publishers | Zero secrets; ephemeral 15-min tokens |
{%- endif %}
{% if include_renovate and include_github -%}
| **Dependency updates** | Renovate | Auto-merge patches; group related updates |
{%- endif %}
| **Git workflow** | Trunk-Based Development | Linear history; squash merges; no GitFlow |

## Development Workflow

```bash
# Format code
uv run ruff format .

# Lint with auto-fix
uv run ruff check . --fix

# Type check
uv run pyright
{% if include_tests %}
# Run tests
uv run pytest --cov=src
{% endif %}
{% if include_pre_commit %}
# Run everything before committing
uv run pre-commit run --all-files
{% endif %}
```

